1ΕΥΡΥΛ

Apparatus criticus

Text after Agostiniani, in Agostiniani, Albanese Procelli 2018.

English translation

Italian translation

commentary

The text is an abbreviation of a personal name, from a Greek onomastic basis formed from Εὐρυ- (Agostiniani 2018, 184; Bechtel 1917, 180-182).
